DOVE
v.
N.C. SUPREME COURT LIBRARY. No. 600P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 6, 2005. Tom Davis, Librarian, for N.C. Supreme Court Library.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 24th day of November 2004 by Plaintiff for Relief:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of April 2005."
